Package mastrbirraio.lib.io

Class IO

  • java.lang.Object
    • mastrbirraio.lib.io.IO
  • public class IO
extends java.lang.Object
    IO is a wrapper static class for all Input/Output operations that allow you to get or print data to console quickly, without handle exception.
    • Print data inline
    • Print data add an endline
    • Get an integer
    • Get a float
    • Get a double
    • Get a string
    • Get a password

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.1
    Author:
    Pino mastrobirraio Matranga
